[Black "Scandinavian 3... Qa5 #5"]
[Result "*"]

1. e4 d5
{ This opening is called Scandinavian Defense. It makes a lot of sense, since from the first move Black fights for central dominance. }
2. exd5
{ 2.e5  is not very good as after  2...c5  White's e5-pawn will become very exposed. Now, after 2. exd5 Black has two different ways of retaking the pawn. }
