O-O Ne7 9. Nb3
{ From this position there is a lot of theory. The bishop can retreat to either b6 or d6 but White has a very slight advantage either way. }
9... Bd6
{ The more popular retreat. This way Black can avoid the exchange of dark-squared bishops. }
10. h3 { I think White does best to prevent ...Bg4. } 10... O-O 11. Bd3 h6 12.
c3
