4. exd5 exd5 5. Bd3
{ This is a slightly better version of the 3. exd5 French, so White has slightly more chances to get an opening advantage because the bishop on b4 is a bit misplaced. However, the knight on c3 is probably also not ideal. I think White can maybe get a very small plus here, so if you want to be safe this is the direction you can look into as White. }
