{ 7.d5  Ne5  and Black is doing fine. The position after @@StartFEN@@r1bqkb1r/pp2pppp/2n2n2/6B1/2pP4/2N5/PP3PPP/R2QKBNR w KQkq - 0 7@@EndFEN@@  7.Bxc4  was considered to be unpleasant for Black until the move  7...h6  was discovered. }
