10... Qc7
{ The most accurate defense, with the idea that after  11.Bd2  c5  12.dxc5  Black can take on c5 with the knight. }
11. O-O { It becomes increasingly difficult to evacuate the e8-king. } 11... b6
{ In case of  11...Nf6  12.Qh4  castling short would lead to disaster for Black. }
